<style>
.tabs-container-{{ section.id}} {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 20px;
}

.tabs-container-{{ section.id}}  .tabs {
  display: flex;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.tabs-container-{{ section.id}}  .tab {
  background: none;
  border: none;
  outline: none;
  padding: 12px 20px;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 16px;
  color: #999;
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
}

.tabs-container-{{ section.id}} .tab.active {
  color: #000;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #ff5722;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.tabs-container-{{ section.id}} .tab-content {
  display: none;
  font-size: 15px;
  color: #333;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.tabs-container-{{ section.id}}  .tab-content.active {
  display: block;
}

.tabs-container-{{ section.id}}  ul {
  margin-top: 10px;
  padding-left: 20px;
}

.tabs-container-{{ section.id}}  ul li {
  list-style-type: disc;
  margin-bottom: 5px;
}
</style>

<div class="tabs-container">
  <div class="tabs">
    <button class="tab active" data-tab="details">Product Details</button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="care">Product Care</button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="fit">Size and Fit</button>
  </div>

  <div class="tab-content active" id="details">
    <p>Experience a sense of edge, luxury, and sophistication with our denim pieces, perfect for this festive season.
    This denim piece made with cotton denim is perfect to offer a sense of style and comfort. It has thread detailing
    around the dress which gives it a great look, along with adjusters and a centre zip for ultimate comfort. This
    dress is a perfect fit for a fun night out this season.</p>

    <p><strong>Product detail</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Cotton denim</li>
      <li>Washed denim</li>
      <li>Comfort stretch denim</li>
      <li>Blue colour</li>
      <li>Ankle length</li>
      <li>Square neck</li>
      <li>Straps with adjusters</li>
      <li>Fastener zipper on centre back with hook and eye and H & O ring on straps</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="tab-content" id="care">
    <p>Hand wash separately in cold water. Do not bleach. Iron on low heat. Dry in shade.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="tab-content" id="fit">
    <p>Model is wearing size S. Model height: 5'8". Fit: Relaxed.</p>
  </div>
</div>

